and hunting through Stack Overflow,

00:06:21.060 --> 00:06:23.140
let's see what chat says about it

00:06:23.200 --> 00:06:24.020
or something like that.

00:06:24.900 --> 00:06:26.300
And then maybe we'll go to Google

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:27.280
if we don't get a good answer.

00:06:27.660 --> 00:06:29.260
Yeah, no, no, I'm the same way.

