I spent more time than I care to admit last night

00:06:33.620 --> 00:06:35.260
migrating from Vim to NeoVim.

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:36.720
And I know I'm late to the party,

00:06:37.200 --> 00:06:38.880
but perplexity and other tools

00:06:38.960 --> 00:06:39.960
just made it a lot easier.

00:06:40.040 --> 00:06:43.820
to start from scratch installation

00:06:44.220 --> 00:06:45.720
without bringing over my VimRC.

