doesn't matter which cell you run, they're never going to get out of date, right?

00:35:08.340 --> 00:35:09.460
Yeah, that's correct.

00:35:09.760 --> 00:35:15.160
So the reactivity, in other words, the data flow graph behind it is the premier feature.

00:35:15.940 --> 00:35:18.600
