00:35:29.840 --> 00:35:32.640
So not only does it like make sure your code and outputs are in sync,

00:35:33.300 --> 00:35:41.960
it also like um makes it really like fun and useful like to it makes it possible to like

00:35:42.010 --> 00:35:46.740
really rapidly experiment with like ideas as long as like your cells aren't too expensive

00:35:47.060 --> 00:35:52.820
if you enable automatic execution then you can change a parameter run the set and run a particular

00:35:53.140 --> 00:36:00.380
cell and i'll run only you know what's required to like um update like subsequent outputs um

00:36:00.900 --> 00:36:13.440
And then another consequence of reactivity that I think is really neat and our users really like is it makes it far easier to use interactive UI widgets than it is in a Jupyter notebook.

00:36:14.460 --> 00:36:21.380
