00:36:49.800 --> 00:36:56.700
like because we know which when you create a UI element as long as you bind it to a global variable

00:36:56.940 --> 00:37:03.700
just say you know my slider equals moda UI.slider then when you interact with the slider and on

00:37:03.940 --> 00:37:09.200
anywhere on the screen well we can just say okay that slider is bound to x we just need to run all

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:14.820
other cells that depend on x and all of a sudden you have really nice interactivity interactive

00:37:14.840 --> 00:37:18.900
elements controlling your code execution without ever having to write a callback.

00:37:20.180 --> 00:37:22.240
